      "para_id": "Q001760.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninmarki , lady of the Munus-gisa , his lady , Ur-Ninĝirsu , ( also called ? ) En-me-zid-ana , the šennu priest , the beloved en priest of Nanše , dedicated this ( statuette ) for the well-being of Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters ."
    }
